creator: DevMM
descriptionHtml:
WHAT IS Kyaw Mal?
Kyaw Mal is a completely free tool where you can create short links, which apart from being free, you get paid! So, now you can make money from home when managing and protecting your links.

This app provides you a custom URL shortener facility to shorten your long links to remember links or branded links.

With this App, you will be able to easily keep track of newly created short URLs and access the analytics within a beautiful interface.

Best Features:

⚡ Full Page Script to convert thousands of the links
⚡ Manage links and edit shorted links anytime
⚡ Multiple withdrawal options for local Myanmar
⚡ One-Click withdrawal
⚡ 2 click URL shorten
⚡ Quick Link Feature
